      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> chopped creamed coconut </strong>and a large pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.3L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
