      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, rinse the <strong>red lentils</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 25-30 min or until the lentils are almost cooked and the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 4,
