    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> halved tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-7 min further or until the tomatoes have softened and the lentils are fully cooked</p><p>Stir most of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (save some for garnish!) through the lentils – this is your <strong>tomato & coconut dal</strong></p>",
