    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>paneer</strong> and cook for 4-5 min</p><p>Add the <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and cook for further 1-2 min or until the paneer is golden – this is your <strong>paprika paneer</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>mini garlic & coriander naans</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
